I read your draft with much interest.
Also outside Industrial Internet there is a wish to have access to a 
standardized routing protocol during the neighbour discovery execution.
I noticed that your draft is rather RPL oriented. Not all companies 
provide RPL in their stack, and it would be interesting to make your 
draft more RPL independent and include other routing protocols as well.
Are you ready to change your draft in that direction?

